{"tid":623359,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[愛情社會經濟學] 從 名校secret 事件, 淺談 網上平台法","createTime":"2018-04-10T02:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T11:58:52.000Z","uid":58377,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9b9a199f47cd597e45e93df76eec5278c51d3c95","tid":623359,"uid":58377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T02:36:44.000Z","msg":"今次唔講愛情 , 轉為講下 連登 vs 名校secret 事件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/205306_85c1ab9657396967778ec5ce8cb625e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F205306_85c1ab9657396967778ec5ce8cb625e6.jpg&h=4a0d8745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n名校secret 修改網民嘅投稿 , 刪留言 , 激嬲咗大家<br />\n<br />\n其實 Facebook , IG , 高登 , 連登 , Amazon , 淘寶 , openrice 甚至 sex141 , 呢類網站都屬於<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「平台式網站」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/205341_16e0322505f8c6f08a32f79f0bf3d28a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F205341_16e0322505f8c6f08a32f79f0bf3d28a.jpg&h=2821a697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今時今日平台式網站無處不在 , 大家係消費前都會上網格價、睇評分、留言 , 甚至 開箱文 , 咁就唔會再好似以前咁 , 因為資訊不足而被廣告或者 sales 誤導<br />\n<br />\n但近年既事件 , 令大家意識到「平台式網站」其實存在好多問題"},{"pid":"1543ffc5f5c001df7b29868e6056b5132a49d7b1","tid":623359,"uid":58377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T02:37:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">平台式網站的兩大隱憂 :  「打手」、「意見造假」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>早前鬧得比較大既「打手事件」有 :</strong><br />\n<br />\n【食評風波】詠藜園：有人推銷打手服務月收三千<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱話/28864/-食評風波-詠藜園-有人推銷打手服務月收三千\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F28864%2F-%E9%A3%9F%E8%A9%95%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E8%A9%A0%E8%97%9C%E5%9C%92-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%8E%A8%E9%8A%B7%E6%89%93%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E6%9C%88%E6%94%B6%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%83&d=cAsawq74O1fdhv4HcXgeOjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=3b9e2ac1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱話/28864/-食評風波-詠藜園-有人推銷打手服務月收三千</a><br />\n<br />\n網民感嘆：Openrice 依家只係餐廳地址搜尋器！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/600976/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/600976/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「打手」可能係出面既人；但「意見造假」就可能係網站管理員 <span style=\"color: orange;\">監守自盜</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n近期就有 香港醫生網 既「操縱評分事件」<br />\n<br />\n著名醫評網涉逼醫生年繳$4,500刪負評 議員質疑敲詐<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171009/57311185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171009%2F57311185&d=cAsawq74O1fdhv4HcXgeOjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=aaa54cdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171009%2F57311185&h=52f0a6e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171009/57311185</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上述事件反映出 平台式網站 最大既問題 :  <span style=\"color: orange;\">冇王管</span><br />\n<br />\n唯一既解決辦法 , 就係制定 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「網上平台法」</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ed4e0d9ea184705be1c635b4f54a66b89eb3e219","tid":623359,"uid":58377,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T02:39:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">網上平台法</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n股評人上到電視節目 , 都會申報自己買咗邊隻股票<br />\n<br />\nWhy ?  因為電視台係<strong>「接觸到好多市民既大平台」</strong><br />\n<br />\n為免影響到社會大眾 , 所以世界各地都會有相關法例去規管電視節目上既言論 , 防止電視台發放 虛假資訊<br />\n<br />\n平台式網站既覆蓋率已經不下於電視台 , 所以政府都應該要設立「網上平台法」去監管 :<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1.  實名制</strong>  -  防止打手</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係 100% 杜絕打手 , 但起碼可以 減少打手帳號 , 從而 增加打手既成本<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>2.  留言鎖</strong>  -  禁止網站自行修改留言</span><br />\n<br />\n做法類似係將網民既留言鎖起 , 然後鎖匙交由政府保管 , 所以任何人 (包括網站自己) 都唔改得<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有觸犯法例既留言 , 網站管理員需要向政府申請開鎖 , 政府批准後就開鎖俾佢 del post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以上就係我既建議。你對於平台式網站又有咩意見？<br />\n大家可以討論一下</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>btw 我寫咗咁多 , 大家不妨俾小弟一個正評 , 以示鼓勵</strong>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b1dca514f434b6a357032ade7a7f89d2bc81f7","tid":623359,"uid":58377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>延伸討論</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">可行的實施方法：政府認證制</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家都知冇可能要求所有平台式網站都交俾政府監管 , 所以其實可以改為 <span style=\"color: orange;\">由網站自行決定係咪交俾政府</span> , 即係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>「政府認證制」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以<strong>「有營食肆」</strong>作例子 , 任何餐廳其實都可以聲稱自己係做健康菜式 , 唔一定要經過政府認證 , 但只要你願意受政府認證 , 你就會獲得「有營食肆」既標誌<br />\n<br />\n所以任何人都可以做個平台式網站出來 , 唔一定要受政府認證 , 但一旦認證咗 , 就要受到網上平台法監管 , 即係要做 <strong>實名制 + 留言鎖</strong>"},{"pid":"c9ce5383776c516addd66380b46c63486c3a8a14","tid":623359,"uid":95519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:27:00.000Z","msg":"留言鎖同gov申請del post<br />\n一來一回咁長時間都已經spread開好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372949583140f73e9042b9d203a43260ffea1493","tid":623359,"uid":58377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9ce5383776c516addd66380b46c63486c3a8a14","tid":623359,"uid":95519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:27:00.000Z","msg":"留言鎖同gov申請del post<br />\n一來一回咁長時間都已經spread開好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:09:57.000Z","msg":"其實負責保管留言鎖既不一定要政府，可以係獨立既機構 or 民間團體，我相信呢啲人既辦事速度都快過政府<br />\n<br />\n當然其實由 出post 到 del post，中間個個時間差通常都已經夠令到個post spread 開，就算網站管理員可以自由 del post，都會有呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n例如以前東方日報控告高登咁，基本上已經係開咗好多個post 之後 阿 Joe 先至 del post"},{"pid":"bd7da881e22b142ab1c8d888a0a4d81911fd4e74","tid":623359,"uid":58377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>延伸討論 2</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「留言鎖」的延伸影響：網站不會再因網民的留言而負上法律責任</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林祖舜成日話因為有巴打既留言內容觸犯法例 , 搞到高登被罰錢<br />\n<br />\n只要將留言鎖交俾政府 , 咁就等於<span style=\"color: orange;\">將法律責任都交埋俾政府</span> , 網站自己唔需要再承擔責任<br />\n<br />\n高登亦都冇得再 del post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">潛在風險：打壓言論、操縱言論</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n「實名制」、「留言鎖」都係 雙面刃 , 因為佢既可以監管網站 , 亦可以成為 打壓言論、操縱言論既工具<br />\n<br />\n所以是否適合用來監管 , 就好視乎地方既政治環境"},{"pid":"a586bed584d65d8e86ee42b2c8e7efe658618fb5","tid":623359,"uid":58377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c6395dcdb81b1e5ca05bd71fe497419dee62c2","tid":623359,"uid":106212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:07:08.000Z","msg":"高質post 留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204f47af88d4f83f32583aab2e6b3491161f617e","tid":623359,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:26:05.000Z","msg":"Dllm實名制<br />\n<br />\n高級五毛？"},{"pid":"b678b4c2ce9b3fa5a8dd3e90e6ce94b54beff7a0","tid":623359,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a586bed584d65d8e86ee42b2c8e7efe658618fb5","tid":623359,"uid":58377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T02:15:21.000Z","msg":"教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ee29ffd67796237eac3ab0bd83a6e232018852","tid":623359,"uid":58377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b678b4c2ce9b3fa5a8dd3e90e6ce9